Description: Linux 4.10-rc5 for 64-bit PCs
 The Linux kernel 4.10-rc5 and modules for use on PCs with AMD64 or Intel
 64 processors.
 .
 This kernel also runs on a Xen hypervisor.  It supports both privileged
 (dom0) and unprivileged (domU) operation.

