Package: linux-headers-4.10.0-rc5-siduction-amd64
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gcc-6
Conflicts: r8168-dkms
Description: Header files for Linux 4.10.0-rc5-siduction-amd64
 This package provides the architecture-specific kernel header files for
 Linux kernel 4.10.0-rc5-siduction-amd64, generally used for building
 out-of-tree kernel modules.  These files are going to be installed into
 /usr/src/linux-headers-4.10.0-rc5-siduction-amd64, and can be used for
 building modules that load into the kernel provided by the
 linux-image-4.10.0-rc5-siduction-amd64 package.

